text: Nizhnyaya Karan-Yelga () is a rural locality (a village) in Kandrinsky Selsoviet, Tuymazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 19 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 44 km from Tuymazy, 27 km from Kandry. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tuymazinsky District
title: Nizhnyaya Karan-Yelga
